Interface Vector<V extends Vector<V>>

Type Parameters:
V - This vector (the result of arithmetic operations)
All Superinterfaces:
Comparable<V>, Numeric, Serializable
All Known Subinterfaces:

All Known Implementing Classes:
Complex, Float2, Float3, Float4, Int2, Int3, Int4, LinearColor, Long2, Long3, Long4, Quaternion, Vector2, Vector3, Vector4, Vertex
public interface Vector<V extends Vector<V>> extends Numeric, Comparable<V>, Serializable
A one-dimensional array of numbers.
